  "title": "Accounts Executive - 6 months temp",
  "description": "<ul><li><p>Execute the migration of historical accounting data (AP, AR, GL) from Excel into the Odoo system based on provided instructions and templates.</p></li><li><p>Accurately perform daily data entry of accounting transactions into the Odoo platform.</p></li><li><p>Verify entered data against source documents for completeness and accuracy.</p></li><li><p>Maintain organized digital records of all migrated and entered data.</p></li><li><p>Process Accounts Payable and Accounts Receivable entries in Odoo as directed.</p></li><li><p>Assist with month-end closing by preparing assigned journal entries and reconciliation schedules.</p></li><li><p>Support the preparation of audit and tax filing documents by compiling requested data from the system.</p></li><li><p>Perform other related data entry and clerical duties to support the finance team.</p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum Diploma in Accountancy or equivalent certification.</p></li><li><p>Minimum 1–2 years of experience in accounting data entry, bookkeeping, or a similar hands-on role.</p></li><li><p>Proficiency in Microsoft Excel (e.g., VLOOKUP, pivot tables). Strong aptitude for working with data and spreadsheets.</p></li><li><p>Hands-on experience with Odoo is necessary</p></li><li><p>Meticulous attention to detail, with a high level of accuracy in data entry and processing.</p></li><li><p>Ability to follow detailed instructions, work systematically on structured tasks, and manage workload effectively.</p></li><li><p>Proactive attitude, good time management, and a reliable, task-oriented work ethic.</p></li></ul>",
